50|$|The News International {{reported}} in December 2011 that <b>the</b> TTP-associated Punjabi <b>Taliban</b> {{had been involved}} in the attack. According to the wife of a Qari Faisal, a slain leader of <b>the</b> Punjabi <b>Taliban,</b> <b>the</b> group had provided the militants with food and logistical support. She also claimed that the militants had been of foreign origin.|$|R
